MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping compares DSPOLICY source data with DSPOLICY_CLONE table (internal to JHIM) with help of trigger table in the joining process. After the compare DSPOLICY_DELTA table is loaded which has record change indicator and field level indicators as well.
MAPPING.NAME: m_COMPARE_LOAD_DSPOLICY_DELTA

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(DATE_DIFF(DATEREVISED_src,DATECREATED_src,'HH')>$$DATEDIFF,'Y','N')
-- If Date revised is greater than Date created by the time/hr value specified in parameter file then session will abort, else it will process.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_DATE_DIFF_IND

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(v_C_MECSTATUSDESC='C' OR v_C_PAIDTODATE='C' OR v_C_TERMINATEDDATE='C' OR v_C_DELIVEREDDATE='C' OR v_C_LINEOFBUSINESS='C' OR v_C_FREELOOKEXP='C' OR v_C_APPRCVDDATE='C' OR v_C_APPSIGDATE='C' OR v_C_POLISSDATE='C' OR v_C_POLYRDATE='C' OR v_C_PRODNAME='C' OR v_C_PRODID='C' OR v_C_CARRID='C' OR v_C_CASEVERSION='C' OR v_C_QUALIFIEDIND='C' --OR v_C_POLICYSTATUSCHANGEDATE='C' --This is system date in HVS end, and this is causing full Update for DSPOLICY --Unless the policy status changes in actual, this field should not be used in comparison OR v_C_FINALSCHDB='C' OR v_C_EXCHANGESTATUS='C' OR v_C_TRADNFOPTION='C' OR v_C_REINSTYPE='C' OR v_C_DIVOPTION='C' OR v_C_SUSPENDCODE='C' OR v_C_ISSUESTATE='C' OR v_C_BILLTODATE='C' OR v_C_LAPSEPREMDUE='C' OR v_C_MECSTATUSDATE='C' OR v_C_POLICYSUSPAMT='C' OR v_C_REINSCOMPNAME='C' OR v_C_TERMCONVDATE='C' OR v_C_POLICYPLANCODE='C' OR v_C_PAIDUPDATE='C' OR v_C_POLICYSTATUS='C' OR v_C_POLICYFEE='C' OR v_C_RPTBLOCKNUM='C' OR v_C_DIVEXCESSOPT = 'C' OR v_C_PREMOFFSETIND = 'C' OR v_C_PREMREFUNDAMT = 'C' OR v_C_DCASTATUS = 'C' OR v_C_LASTANNDATE = 'C' OR v_C_BANDID = 'C' OR v_C_REBALANCEIND = 'C' OR v_C_INDIVOWN = 'C' OR v_C_DTHCERTRCVD = 'C' OR v_C_PRODUCTTYPE = 'C' OR v_C_REPLACEMENTDESC='C' OR v_C_TERMENDDATE='C' OR v_C_CNTRBPROCTYPE='C' OR v_C_NFOCMBTYPE='C' OR v_C_MATURITYDATE='C' OR v_C_TradEVOption='C' OR v_C_PRDVARID='C' OR v_C_REINSAMT='C' OR v_C_DEATHNOTIFYDATE='C' OR v_C_PRROWID='C', 'C','NC')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_change_ind

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER_src) AND NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER), 'D', NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER_src) AND ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER), $$CDC_IND_INS, NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER_src) AND NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER) AND v_change_ind='NC','X', NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER_src) AND NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER) and (v_change_ind='C'),$$CDC_IND_UPD )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: o_REC_IND

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, CDC_IND_src='C' and ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER),'1010', --CDC_IND_src='I' and NOT ISNULL(POLICYNUMBER),'1020', '1')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_ERROR_CODE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(TRUE, v_ERROR_CODE='1010','No record not found in Clone table for this changed record', v_ERROR_CODE='1020','A record is already present in Clone table for this new insert record', NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: o_ERROR_DESCRIPTION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(v_ERROR_CODE='1010' AND v_DATE_DIFF_IND='Y', ABORT('It cannot be flagged as UPDATE in the DELTA table as no record is present in DSPOLICY_CLONE table for Policynumber -'||POLICYNUMBER_src),'1')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: o_ABORT_IND
